  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1997-04-10", 
    "text": "Senior Homeowner Reverse Mortgage Protection Act - Amends the National Housing Act with respect to home equity conversion mortgages to: (1) require full disclosure to the mortgagor of all mortgage costs, including estate planning, financial advice, or other related costs; and (2) provide for imposition of restrictions by the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to ensure that the mortgagor is not charged for such costs."
  }, 
